  "texts": [
    "Simultaneously, breakthroughs in deep learning technology have led to a shift towards deep learning in NLP, yielding significant accomplishments.",
    "The standardization of corpora and the application of deep learning techniques have attracted more attention to ABSA, fostering the development of numerous exceptional systems and models.",
    "Nevertheless, ABSA remains a challenging task.",
    "Textual SA can be divided into explicit SA and implicit SA.",
    "Much of the research is concentrated in the domain of explicit SA."
  ]
}